==Bundles==
Dandelion is used in the {{Bundle|Spring Foraging||y}}.

==Tailoring==
Dandelion is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{name|Shirt002|link=Tailoring{{!}}Mint Blouse|class=inline}}. It is a yellow dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the yellow dye pot at [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]], for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*Dandelion may be randomly requested during [[Spring]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|120}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}

